---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Demo">
  <p>See Turbo Themes in action. These demos show how the same design tokens work across different setups.</p>

  <h2>Integration Examples</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Minimal (Recommended)</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>The simplest setup. Just Turbo Themes CSS variables - no framework, no build step.</p>
        <div class="stats" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">~10KB</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Total CSS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Dependencies</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="/demo/minimal/" class="btn btn-primary">View Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Bulma Integration</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>For existing Bulma projects. The adapter maps Turbo tokens to Bulma's internal variables.</p>
        <div class="stats" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">~250KB</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Total CSS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">Bulma</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Framework</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="/demo/with-bulma/" class="btn btn-primary">View Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Tailwind Integration</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>For existing Tailwind projects. Adds Turbo colors as utility classes like <code>bg-turbo-primary</code>.</p>
        <div class="stats" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">~15KB</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Total CSS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">Tailwind</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Framework</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-footer">
        <a href="/demo/with-tailwind/" class="btn btn-primary">View Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>How It Works</h2>

  <p>
    Turbo Themes provides <strong>CSS Custom Properties</strong> (variables) that define your color palette.
    Use them directly in your CSS:
  </p>

  <pre><code class="language-css">.my-button &#123;
  background: var(--turbo-brand-primary);
  color: var(--turbo-text-inverse);
  border: 1px solid var(--turbo-border-default);
&#125;</code></pre>

  <p>
    If you're already using Bulma or Tailwind, the adapters let you keep using those frameworks
    while benefiting from Turbo's theme system.
  </p>

  <h3>Theme Switching</h3>

  <p>
    Switch themes by changing the <code>data-theme</code> attribute and loading the corresponding CSS file:
  </p>

  <pre><code class="language-js">// Switch to Dracula theme
document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dracula');
document.getElementById('turbo-theme-css').href = '/assets/css/themes/turbo/dracula.css';
localStorage.setItem('turbo-theme', 'dracula');</code></pre>

  <h2>Complete Examples</h2>

  <p>
    Want to see more? Check out our <a href="/examples/">complete examples</a> for React, Vue, Bootstrap,
    and more. Each example includes full source code, tests, and StackBlitz playgrounds.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
    <a href="/examples/" class="btn btn-outline">View All Examples</a>
    <a href="https://stackblitz.com/github/TurboCoder13/turbo-themes/tree/main/examples/stackblitz/react" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try React Example</a>
    <a href="https://stackblitz.com/github/TurboCoder13/turbo-themes/tree/main/examples/stackblitz/vue" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try Vue Example</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
